title: Late Late Nigh Fever Mix
text:
Fyrsta mixið með SL-1200 plötuspilurunum mínum, svolítið leiðinlegt pitch ctrl í gangi en enjoy :)
http://soundcloud.com/birgiss/va-birgiss-latelatefevermix
(Hægt er að downloada þaðan)
Lengd: 1:01:49 min
Bitrate: 128kbps
bpm: 123-126
Stefnur: Minimal, Deep House, Tech House
Lagalisti:
1. Marc Antona - Cotton
2. Sasse & James Flavour - Comfort Zone
3. Fog - Playin' Low
4. Butane Feat. Midnight - Damned Lecherious Old Men (Bruno Pronsato Remix)
5. Reboot - Me Show
6. Davide Squillace - What About The Vice
7. Grunbox - Share The Bong (Guti Remix)
8. Paul C, Paolo Martini - Plug (Johnny D Remix)
9. Mikael Stavostrand - Send Me Signs
10. Reset Robot - Tresoli
11. John Dimas - Lost In The Clouds
12. Groove Armada - Paper Romance (Kruse & Nuremberg Remix)
13. El Mundo and Satori and Kid Culture - Gotta Help (Mendo Remix)
14. Johnny D - Triva Mango
